h3 Floating labels
p.-text
  | Floating labels are a solution to keep the placeholder visible when no label is attached to the input.
  | Lux only supports floating labels on <code>-lg</code> and <code>-xl</code> inputs.

.example.-mb--3
  .-p--3
    each size in ['lg', 'xl']
      div(class=`lux-col -w--12 -p--2`)
        .lux-input__wrapper.-floating-label(style="max-width:20rem")
          input(type="text", class=`lux-input -${size} -mr--3`, id=`floating-label-${size}`)
          label(for=`floating-label-${size}`) Placeholder text
  .example-tabs.-pl--2
    ul.lux-tabs#example-input-floating-label
